her constraints)\n88. Not attempted due to medical conditions or safety concerms\n1.\nSOC/ROC\nPerformance\nEnter Codes\nin Boxes\n\u4e2a\nEating: The ability to use suitable utensils to bring food and/or liquid to the mouth and swallow food and/or\nliquid once the meal is placed before the patient.", "type": "Document"}}